Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞会定在下雪天也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是圣诞节在二十二日这天也真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十三与二十四日学校放假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs22}人符「现世斩」 囧rz
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无道 无道 无道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(165,165)\shad3\fad(300,300)\be1}土豆5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,385)\shad3\fad(300,300)\be1}平安夜的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样暖和些了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法 被你发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 当然好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 你也吃个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蛋糕棒 是昨天才发售的新品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森山同学 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待呢 今天的圣诞会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说小京会做点心来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 就算不是圣诞会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于一直给予我精神的森山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是我的圣诞老人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子究竟能装下多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类只要有正确的心态就可能在任何的环境下生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如 明治三十五年…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs22}好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs22}校长话真长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs22}真想快点去温暖的教室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去暖暖身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先一步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面真的好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你自己要硬撑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛蛋黄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明这里有点心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是小京自己做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕卷 饼干 螺钉巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连鸡丁沙拉也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷你松露玉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那玩意儿哪迷你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 要吃一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么来尝尝松露玉的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 松露子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两只动物看来不太友好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是在抢食物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来尝尝我的糖果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的 该怎么说呢 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且拒绝接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常大量的松露球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也喂我吃一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,420)\fad(200,30)}{\fs22\shad0\1c&6bb138&\3c&H000000&}坏心眼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,30)}松露子败北
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在宣布圣诞会的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 不要干多余的事速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 谁来帮忙装饰下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 在这装上长条诗笺的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是小英啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,築濑　蛋糕一共就三个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么班长 干杯前的音头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位拿上杯子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没忘记什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能想起老师我来 我真高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我存在感真低啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃这么多没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点到为止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来年再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄子真健壮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为身体很软吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野性动物真神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子会把自己的孩子推下山谷是骗人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在电视看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热带大草原里可没有什么山谷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没听过那事 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 森山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来年再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始就是寒假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音音还是和以往一样要去海外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今年是去意大利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那个吧 蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为放寒假了 所以与森山见不到面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在想不能大意让*『消音处理』毛长太长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该是已经长出来了正在烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松露子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了的话就来我这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京你在干什么啊 聚会要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦 别感冒咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小家伙 明明都说不需要谢礼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为放寒假了 所以与森山见不到面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来买圣诞蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里的好吃些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是机会啊 蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出勇气来邀请他参加我家的聚会看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 森山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有时间的话就来我家参加聚会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强 竟然吃掉了我才买的啤酒夹心蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs22}距离今年结束还有一小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs22}在寺院敲响的钟声之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs22}有许多人聚集在点亮的灯笼之间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs22}记者山田小姐 你那边情况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs22}是 这里是身处现场的山田…
